### Groceries API Endpoints

# Get all groceries
GET https://cse-341-final-project-z4pd.onrender.com/groceries/
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Get grocery by ID (replace {id} with actual grocery ID)
GET https://cse-341-final-project-z4pd.onrender.com/groceries/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Create a new grocery item
POST https://cse-341-final-project-z4pd.onrender.com/groceries/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Apples",
    "quantity": 5,
    "price": 2.99
}

###

# Create another grocery item
POST https://cse-341-final-project-z4pd.onrender.com/groceries/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Bananas",
    "quantity": 10,
    "price": 1.49
}

###

# Create a grocery item with decimal values
POST https://cse-341-final-project-z4pd.onrender.com/groceries/
Content-Type: application/json

